data.description: Look no further! This is the perfect family home in the sought-after Silver City Elementary and N. Forsyth High School District. Gorgeous eat-in kitchen w/ granite countertops, 42" cabinets, open view to fireside family room, gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the main level & upgraded carpet throughout the upstairs. Upstairs has oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets and lots of storage space throughout. Master suite w/ sitting area, his & her walk-in closets and an oversized bathroom with double vanities, walk-in shower and garden tub. Bedroom on main perfect for office/guest room. Enjoy the backyard under your private covered patio or take the landscaped stairs down to the custom stone patio with firepit & hammock at water's edge to enjoy the beautiful sunsets.  Brand new roof and professionally landscaped yard w/ 2 mature Japanese maples.  Walking distance to pool/tennis/basketball/pickleball/playground. Minutes from the Outlet Mall, dining, Lake Lanier, North GA Mountains, and easy, quick access to GA 400.
